" />"},{"pid":"e576093dcf75fd5fa0f3be7c9d8417996a081117","tid":208550,"uid":102121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>新地樂根本就唔應該出現<br />\n兩樣溝埋都唔夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實好似得香港m記先有呢樣野<br />\n味道唔錯既個人認為</blockquote><br />\n美國機場見到有賣一樣嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n我覺得幾好飲喎<br />\n成日自己去超市買汽水雪糕溝埋<br />\n當飯後甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係m記隻杯裡面有冰先麻煩 次次雪糕痴住晒"},{"pid":"6ecf48d609ff88a52551e917f013cf6fcc3bd08e","tid":208550,"uid":55192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"\b有冇人試過 一野插咗啲新地落可樂度 然後大爆炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n我有次係整跌咗個杯 啲汽水一同新地撞埋即刻\b變泡大爆炸 一褲都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起個時試過叫新地樂走冰 個職員唔俾"},{"pid":"3757840e02586cdeb6f59c3f4078b60b9c3a1603","tid":208550,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"溝埋黎飲"},{"pid":"74fc341e5e5e6d8b573b6207e2de7120594a50db","tid":208550,"uid":66740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:04:53.000Z","msg":"無冰點樣浪起d雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef1127c6d22efcbe44ba69979fd5d9119fac1a0","tid":208550,"uid":16384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T22:51:22.000Z","msg":"溝埋變雲呢拿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e20f05afc847f220d335a1d308b7c83eb098d84","tid":208550,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T22:53:33.000Z","msg":"其實隻味有啲似雲呢拿可樂"},{"pid":"2d2ebc0d8bb44ef8271944bb3be85876392f49f2","tid":208550,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T00